.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-8-2::.
There 7 different types of food: artichoke, banana, cabbage, corn, lettuce, orange, plum
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, coach, entrepreneur, lawyer, manager, musician, scientist
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, adventure, family, horror, mystery, romance, zombie
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cycling, surfing, biathlon, parkour, tennis, rugby, water-polo
 1. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
 2. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
 3. the coach is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 4. the lawyer is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is not the bartender##6
 6. the person eating orange is somewhere between the bartender and the person who's sport is surfing##7
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##5
 8. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the manager##5
 9. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
10. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the entrepreneur##5
11. the person eating lettuce is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
12. the lawyer is somewhere to the left of the entrepreneur##5
13. the person watching romance movies is somewhere between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching family movies##7
14. the musician is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8
15. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
16. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
17. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
18. the musician is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
19. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
20. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
21. the bartender is somewhere to the right of the entrepreneur##5
22. the musician is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
23. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the person eating banana and the person watching family movies##7
24. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating corn##5
25. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
26. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
27. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the right of the person eating plum##8
28. the person eating corn is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
29. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4
30. the person eating cabbage is not to the right of the lawyer##8
31. the musician is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
32. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
33. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
34. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

